column5: I may be renting a cottage property on this lake, but I have never heard of it or if it has any fishing opportunities.  It is in the muskoka and Haliburton area, near lake of bays. Does anyone have any information about this lake, anything at all would help.  Lakeshore

Was lucky enough to be granted access on that Lake one day, about 5 years ago. There is no public access (I checked with our local C.O.)  Fantastic Smallmouth, can't remember if we caught any largemouth or not but the Smallies were amazing. Have a blast.  Hookset.
